<template>
  <CDynamicForm
    ref="elForm"
    :formData="model"
    :form-items="formItems"
    :form-attrs="formAttrs"
  >
  </CDynamicForm>
</template>

<script>
import CDynamicForm from '@/components/common/CDynamicForm';
export default {
  name: 'TestForm',
  components: {
    CDynamicForm
  },
  props: {
    /**
     * 表单数据
     */
    formData: {
      type: Object,
      default: () => ({})
    }
  },
  mounted() {
    this.extendElFormMethods();
  },
  data() {
    return {
      /** 表单数据 */
      model: {},
      /** 表单项 */
      formItems: [
        {
          type: 'input',
          prop: 'name',
          label: '姓名',
          rules: {
            required: true,
            trigger: 'blur',
            message: '请填写姓名'
          }
        },
        {
          type: 'input',
          prop: 'age',
          label: '年龄'
        }
      ],
      /**
       * 表单属性
       */
      formAttrs: {
        'label-width': '120px'
      }
    };
  },
  watch: {
    model() {
      this.$emit('change-model', this.model);
    },
    formData() {
      this.model = this.formData;
    }
  },
  methods: {
    /**
     * 继承ElForm组件方法
     */
    extendElFormMethods() {
      let elForm = this.$refs.elForm;
      ['validate', 'validateField', 'resetFields', 'clearValidate'].forEach(
        key => {
          let methods = elForm[key];
          typeof methods === 'function' && (this[key] = methods);
        }
      );
    }
  }
};
</script>
